Hi Lucas,

We have just received an update from our colleagues on this.

They asked the following:

1. I the customer can create a Snapshot of the EPP server(if possible) from their VM or AWS/Azure/GCP platform.
2. If the customer can Upgrade the EPP server to the latest version 5.9.4.1.
3. If the customer can upgrade the EPP agent to the latest line/production agent and then try again to see if it works.

Also please ask them to also try without Deep Packet Inspection enabled and see if it works for them.

We checked some Microsoft forums and we found several cases where people complained about having issues when using Regex with Outlook.

Please let us know if the issue still persists after doing the above mentioned steps.

Best Regards,
